You know what 2019 was the opening year for me as an outsider watching UK Grime/drill scene, before that time I only knew Santan Dave (Bug up to him), Skepta, It might my missperspective that I was thinking yo this uk scene is mad, then I started to know more and more drill MC's, which I considered dope, but now after hearing Wiley's Eediyat Skengman, I started to discover more and more Giant MC's like Dot Rotten, Yungen, Wiley as well, and more. But this Dot Rotten he is a Don. Now I realized that all them yutes whom I was listening are just trifles comparing to those heavyweight chapmions. Word!
No matter what I bet UK scene is mazza! Shout out to you guys from Kazkahstan!
